        },
        "story-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Ledgerworks was founded in 2011 by Karen Whitfield with a simple observation: small businesses deserve the same caliber of financial guidance as Fortune 500 companies. What started as a one-person practice in downtown Boston has grown into an eight-person firm serving over 500 clients.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        },
        "story-text-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We invest in technology and talent so our clients get proactive advice — not just year-end reports. Every engagement starts with understanding your business, not your ledger.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        }
      },
